headline: Exponent (EXPO) Q3 Earnings and Revenues Top Estimates
summary: Exponent (EXPO) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +10.00% and +4.38%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: Data Theorem Ranked #1 for Cloud-Native Use Case in the 2025 Gartner® Critical Capabilities for Application Security Testing Report
summary: Data Theorem, Inc., a leading provider of modern application security testing and protection solutions for cloud-native, web, mobile, and API-based applications, today announced that it was ranked #1 for both the Cloud-Native Use Case and API security capabilities in the 2025 Gartner Critical Capabilities for Application Security Testing report.
